          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Inclusion criteria: o Patient admitted to a standard hospital department within the past 72 hrs, o Age > 18 years, o Covid-19 diagnosis confirmed by positive RT-PCR o Patient agreeing to take part in the study o Patient registered with a social security scheme  "
          },
          {
            "clusion": "E",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": "o Hospitalisation en soins critiques (réanimation ou soins intensifs) préalable pendant plus de 72h car risque de biais d’analyse de l’état nutritionnel"
          },
